        {
            "role": "assistant",
            "content": "{\"message\":\"Continuing the STRIDE\u2010per\u2010element analysis for the remaining Processes, Data Stores, and Data Flows.\",\"threats\":[{\"id\":18,\"element\":\"Blog Application API\",\"threat_description\":\"Attacker uses stolen API key to masquerade as a valid client.\",\"element_type\":\"Process\",\"stride\":\"Spoofing\",\"Mitre ATT&CK\":\"T1550: Use of Valid Accounts\",\"OWASP Top 10\":\"A07:2021\",\"mitigation\":\"Rotate and scope API keys; enforce mTLS or signed requests.\",\"cvss_vector\":\"AV:N/AC:L/PR:L/UI:N/S:U/C:H/I:H/A:L\"},{\"id\":19,\"element\":\"Blog Application API\",\"threat_description\":\"Adversary tampers with JSON payload to alter data operations.\",\"element_type\":\"Process\",\"stride\":\"Tampering\",\"Mitre ATT&CK\":\"T1490: Inhibit System Recovery\",\"OWASP Top 10\":\"A03:2021\",\"mitigation\":\"Validate and sanitize payloads; use parameterized calls.\",\"cvss_vector\":\"AV:N/AC:L/PR:N/UI:N/S:U/C:H/I:H/A:N\"},{\"id\":20,\"element\":\"Blog Application API\",\"threat_description\":\"Lack of request/response logging enables denial of API calls performed.\",\"element_type\":\"Process\",\"stride\":\"Repudiation\",\"Mitre ATT&CK\":\"T1071: Application Layer Protocol\",\"OWASP Top 10\":\"A09:2021\",\"mitigation\":\"Implement immutable, timestamped API logs with request IDs.\",\"cvss_vector\":\"AV:N/AC:L/PR:N/UI:N/S:U/C:N/I:N/A:N\"},{\"id\":21,\"element\":\"Blog Application API\",\"threat_description\":\"Detailed error stack traces reveal internal code structure.\",\"element_type\":\"Process\",\"stride\":\"Information Disclosure\",\"Mitre ATT&CK\":\"T1552: Unsecured Credentials\",\"OWASP Top 10\":\"A05:2021\",\"mitigation\":\"Disable detailed errors; return generic messages.\",\"cvss_vector\":\"AV:N/AC:L/PR:N/UI:N/S:U/C:L/I:N/A:N\"},{\"id\":22,\"element\":\"Blog Application API\",\"threat_description\":\"Flooding API endpoints exhausts function concurrency and downstream resources.\",\"element_type\":\"Process\",\"stride\":\"Denial of Service\",\"Mitre ATT&CK\":\"T1499: Endpoint Denial of Service\",\"OWASP Top 10\":null,\"mitigation\":\"Apply rate limits, circuit breakers, and WAF protection.\",\"cvss_vector\":\"AV:N/AC:L/PR:N/UI:N/S:C/C:N/I:N/A:H\"},{\"id\":23,\"element\":\"Blog Application API\",\"threat_description\":\"Misconfigured role assignment allows API to perform unauthorized actions.\",\"element_type\":\"Process\",\"stride\":\"Elevation of Privilege\",\"Mitre ATT&CK\":\"T1548: Abuse Elevation Control Mechanism\",\"OWASP Top 10\":\"A05:2021\",\"mitigation\":\"Enforce least-privilege on managed identity; regular RBAC reviews.\",\"cvss_vector\":\"AV:N/AC:H/PR:H/UI:N/S:U/C:N/I:N/A:N\"},{\"id\":24,\"element\":\"Development Instance\",\"threat_description\":\"Impersonation of the container instance to push malicious builds.\",\"element_type\":\"Process\",\"stride\":\"Spoofing\",\"Mitre ATT&CK\":\"T1587.002: Hijack Execution Flow: DLL Side-Loading\",\"OWASP Top 10\":\"A08:2021\",\"mitigation\":\"Authenticate container instance via certificates; validate build source.\",\"cvss_vector\":\"AV:N/AC:M/PR:N/UI:N/S:U/C:H/I:H/A:N\"},{\"id\":25,\"element\":\"Development Instance\",\"threat_description\":\"Tampering of deployment scripts or build artifacts before deployment.\",\"element_type\":\"Process\",\"stride\":\"Tampering\",\"Mitre ATT&CK\":\"T1059.003: Windows Command Shell\",\"OWASP Top 10\":\"A03:2021\",\"mitigation\":\"Sign and verify artifacts; enforce pipeline code reviews.\",\"cvss_vector\":\"AV:N/AC:L/PR:N/UI:N/S:U/C:H/I:H/A:N\"},{\"id\":26,\"element\":\"Development Instance\",\"threat_description\":\"Container actions not logged allow repudiation of changes to prod infra.\",\"element_type\":\"Process\",\"stride\":\"Repudiation\",\"Mitre ATT&CK\":\"T1078: Valid Accounts\",\"OWASP Top 10\":\"A09:2021\",\"mitigation\":\"Enable container activity logs with integrity checks.\",\"cvss_vector\":\"AV:N/AC:L/PR:N/UI:N/S:U/C:N/I:N/A:N\"},{\"id\":27,\"element\":\"Development Instance\",\"threat_description\":\"Sensitive environment variables (keys) leak via container logs.\",\"element_type\":\"Process\",\"stride\":\"Information Disclosure\",\"Mitre ATT&CK\":\"T1552: Unsecured Credentials\",\"OWASP Top 10\":\"A02:2021\",\"mitigation\":\"Redact secrets from logs; use managed identities.\",\"cvss_vector\":\"AV:N/AC:L/PR:N/UI:N/S:U/C:L/I:N/A:N\"},{\"id\":28,\"element\":\"Development Instance\",\"threat_description\":\"Overconsumption of CPU/memory by build processes causes pipeline failure.\",\"element_type\":\"Process\",\"stride\":\"Denial of Service\",\"Mitre ATT&CK\":\"T1499: Endpoint Denial of Service\",\"OWASP Top 10\":null,\"mitigation\":\"Resource quotas, autoscaling, and health probes.\",\"cvss_vector\":\"AV:N/AC:L/PR:N/UI:N/S:C/C:N/I:N/A:H\"},{\"id\":29,\"element\":\"Development Instance\",\"threat_description\":\"Compromised instance elevates to Contributor across the Dev Resource Group.\",\"element_type\":\"Process\",\"stride\":\"Elevation of Privilege\",\"Mitre ATT&CK\":\"T1548: Abuse Elevation Control Mechanism\",\"OWASP Top 10\":null,\"mitigation\":\"Assign minimal roles; use separate service principals for pipeline.\",\"cvss_vector\":\"AV:N/AC:L/PR:H/UI:N/S:U/C:N/I:N/A:N\"},{\"id\":30,\"element\":\"Automation Account\",\"threat_description\":\"Adversary spoofs the automation account identity to run arbitrary scripts.\",\"element_type\":\"Process\",\"stride\":\"Spoofing\",\"Mitre ATT&CK\":\"T1078: Valid Accounts\",\"OWASP Top 10\":\"A07:2021\",\"mitigation\":\"Use strong authentication (managed identity); rotate keys.\",\"cvss_vector\":\"AV:N/AC:L/PR:N/UI:N/S:U/C:H/I:H/A:L\"},{\"id\":31,\"element\":\"Automation Account\",\"threat_description\":\"Runbook code is tampered with to deploy malicious resources.\",\"element_type\":\"Process\",\"stride\":\"Tampering\",\"Mitre ATT&CK\":\"T1059.006: Graphical User Interface\",\"OWASP Top 10\":\"A03:2021\",\"mitigation\":\"Store runbooks in secure repo; enforce code signing.\",\"cvss_vector\":\"AV:N/AC:L/PR:N/UI:N/S:U/C:H/I:H/A:N\"},{\"id\":32,\"element\":\"Automation Account\",\"threat_description\":\"Lack of runbook execution logs allows repudiation of changes made.\",\"element_type\":\"Process\",\"stride\":\"Repudiation\",\"Mitre ATT&CK\":\"T1078: Valid Accounts\",\"OWASP Top 10\":\"A09:2021\",\"mitigation\":\"Enable audit logs for all runbook actions in Log Analytics.\",\"cvss_vector\":\"AV:N/AC:L/PR:N/UI:N/S:U/C:N/I:N/A:N\"},{\"id\":33,\"element\":\"Automation Account\",\"threat_description\":\"Runbook outputs include plain\u2010text secrets from Key Vault.\",\"element_type\":\"Process\",\"stride\":\"Information Disclosure\",\"Mitre ATT&CK\":\"T1552: Unsecured Credentials\",\"OWASP Top 10\":\"A02:2021\",\"mitigation\":\"Mask secrets in logs; limit verbose output.\",\"cvss_vector\":\"AV:N/AC:L/PR:N/UI:N/S:U/C:L/I:N/A:N\"},{\"id\":34,\"element\":\"Automation Account\",\"threat_description\":\"Mass triggering of runbooks exhausts automation throughput.\",\"element_type\":\"Process\",\"stride\":\"Denial of Service\",\"Mitre ATT&CK\":\"T1499: Endpoint Denial of Service\",\"OWASP Top 10\":null,\"mitigation\":\"Throttle runbook triggers; implement approval workflows.\",\"cvss_vector\":\"AV:N/AC:L/PR:N/UI:N/S:C/C:N/I:N/A:H\"},{\"id\":35,\"element\":\"Automation Account\",\"threat_description\":\"Compromised account elevates privileges to Owner on production RG.\",\"element_type\":\"Process\",\"stride\":\"Elevation of Privilege\",\"Mitre ATT&CK\":\"T1548: Abuse Elevation Control Mechanism\",\"OWASP Top 10\":null,\"mitigation\":\"Use separate least-privileged service principal for prod; monitor RBAC changes.\",\"cvss_vector\":\"AV:N/AC:L/PR:H/UI:N/S:U/C:N/I:N/A:N\"},{\"id\":36,\"element\":\"Application Resource Storage Container\",\"threat_description\":\"Malicious actor modifies static assets or config blobs.\",\"element_type\":\"Data Store\",\"stride\":\"Tampering\",\"Mitre ATT&CK\":\"T1565: Data Manipulation\",\"OWASP Top 10\":\"A08:2021\",\"mitigation\":\"Enable blob immutability policies and SAS tokens with write restrictions.\",\"cvss_vector\":\"AV:N/AC:L/PR:N/UI:N/S:U/C:H/I:H/A:N\"},{\"id\":37,\"element\":\"Application Resource Storage Container\",\"threat_description\":\"Uploader denies having changed configuration blobs.\",\"element_type\":\"Data Store\",\"stride\":\"Repudiation\",\"Mitre ATT&CK\":\"T1099: Data from Local System\",\"OWASP Top 10\":\"A09:2021\",\"mitigation\":\"Enable Storage Analytics logs with read/write auditing.\",\"cvss_vector\":\"AV:N/AC:L/PR:N/UI:N/S:U/C:N/I:N/A:N\"},{\"id\":38,\"element\":\"Application Resource Storage Container\",\"threat_description\":\"Public access to container leaks environment configuration.\",\"element_type\":\"Data Store\",\"stride\":\"Information Disclosure\",\"Mitre ATT&CK\":\"T1537: Transfer Data to Cloud Account\",\"OWASP Top 10\":\"A02:2021\",\"mitigation\":\"Disable public access; enforce private endpoints.\",\"cvss_vector\":\"AV:N/AC:L/PR:N/UI:N/S:U/C:H/I:N/A:N\"},{\"id\":39,\"element\":\"Application Resource Storage Container\",\"threat_description\":\"Excessive read/write requests throttle access for legitimate users.\",\"element_type\":\"Data Store\",\"stride\":\"Denial of Service\",\"Mitre ATT&CK\":\"T1499: Endpoint Denial of Service\",\"OWASP Top 10\":null,\"mitigation\":\"Apply storage account throttling, SAS token limits, and monitoring.\",\"cvss_vector\":\"AV:N/AC:L/PR:N/UI:N/S:C/C:N/I:N/A:H\"},{\"id\":40,\"element\":\"Dev Storage Container\",\"threat_description\":\"Injection of malicious build artifacts into Dev container.\",\"element_type\":\"Data Store\",\"stride\":\"Tampering\",\"Mitre ATT&CK\":\"T1574: Hijack Execution Flow\",\"OWASP Top 10\":\"A08:2021\",\"mitigation\":\"Restrict write access; scan blobs for malware.\",\"cvss_vector\":\"AV:N/AC:L/PR:N/UI:N/S:U/C:H/I:H/A:N\"},{\"id\":41,\"element\":\"Dev Storage Container\",\"threat_description\":\"No audit trail of who uploaded or modified artifacts.\",\"element_type\":\"Data Store\",\"stride\":\"Repudiation\",\"Mitre ATT&CK\":\"T1099: Data from Local System\",\"OWASP Top 10\":\"A09:2021\",\"mitigation\":\"Enable blob-level auditing and alert on changes.\",\"cvss_vector\":\"AV:N/AC:L/PR:N/UI:N/S:U/C:N/I:N/A:N\"},{\"id\":42,\"element\":\"Dev Storage Container\",\"threat_description\":\"Access to build artifacts discloses proprietary code.\",\"element_type\":\"Data Store\",\"stride\":\"Information Disclosure\",\"Mitre ATT&CK\":\"T1537: Transfer Data to Cloud Account\",\"OWASP Top 10\":\"A02:2021\",\"mitigation\":\"Use private endpoints and RBAC; encrypt at rest.\",\"cvss_vector\":\"AV:N/AC:L/PR:N/UI:N/S:U/C:H/I:N/A:N\"},{\"id\":43,\"element\":\"Dev Storage Container\",\"threat_description\":\"Bulk uploads of large blobs exhaust storage capacity.\",\"element_type\":\"Data Store\",\"stride\":\"Denial of Service\",\"Mitre ATT&CK\":\"T1499: Endpoint Denial of Service\",\"OWASP Top 10\":null,\"mitigation\":\"Quota on container size; monitor metrics.\",\"cvss_vector\":\"AV:N/AC:L/PR:N/UI:N/S:C/C:N/I:N/A:H\"},{\"id\":44,\"element\":\"Resource Group\",\"threat_description\":\"Attacker modifies resource configurations (VM, Functions).\",\"element_type\":\"Data Store\",\"stride\":\"Tampering\",\"Mitre ATT&CK\":\"T1578.002: Hijack Execution Flow\",\"OWASP Top 10\":\"A05:2021\",\"mitigation\":\"Lock critical resources; enable RBAC with MFA.\",\"cvss_vector\":\"AV:N/AC:L/PR:H/UI:N/S:U/C:H/I:H/A:N\"},{\"id\":45,\"element\":\"Resource Group\",\"threat_description\":\"Changes to resources go unlogged, enabling repudiation.\",\"element_type\":\"Data Store\",\"stride\":\"Repudiation\",\"Mitre ATT&CK\":\"T1078: Valid Accounts\",\"OWASP Top 10\":\"A09:2021\",\"mitigation\":\"Enable Azure Activity Logs with retention and alerts.\",\"cvss_vector\":\"AV:N/AC:L/PR:N/UI:N/S:U/C:N/I:N/A:N\"},{\"id\":46,\"element\":\"Resource Group\",\"threat_description\":\"Metadata about deployed services disclosed via API endpoints.\",\"element_type\":\"Data Store\",\"stride\":\"Information Disclosure\",\"Mitre ATT&CK\":\"T1537: Transfer Data to Cloud Account\",\"OWASP Top 10\":\"A05:2021\",\"mitigation\":\"Restrict resource discovery APIs; use private links.\",\"cvss_vector\":\"AV:N/AC:L/PR:L/UI:N/S:U/C:L/I:N/A:N\"},{\"id\":47,\"element\":\"Resource Group\",\"threat_description\":\"Mass deletion or stop commands render production unavailable.\",\"element_type\":\"Data Store\",\"stride\":\"Denial of Service\",\"Mitre ATT&CK\":\"T1499: Endpoint Denial of Service\",\"OWASP Top 10\":null,\"mitigation\":\"Apply resource locks and multi-user approvals.\",\"cvss_vector\":\"AV:N/AC:L/PR:H/UI:N/S:C/C:N/I:N/A:H\"},{\"id\":48,\"element\":\"Function Code\",\"threat_description\":\"Unauthorized modification of code packages before execution.\",\"element_type\":\"Data Store\",\"stride\":\"Tampering\",\"Mitre ATT&CK\":\"T1505: Server Software Component\",\"OWASP Top 10\":\"A03:2021\",\"mitigation\":\"Code signing and validation at runtime.\",\"cvss_vector\":\"AV:N/AC:L/PR:N/UI:N/S:U/C:H/I:H/A:N\"},{\"id\":49,\"element\":\"Function Code\",\"threat_description\":\"Changes to code not tracked or logged, enabling repudiation.\",\"element_type\":\"Data Store\",\"stride\":\"Repudiation\",\"Mitre ATT&CK\":\"T1071: Application Layer Protocol\",\"OWASP Top 10\":\"A09:2021\",\"mitigation\":\"Use version control with immutable history and alert on changes.\",\"cvss_vector\":\"AV:N/AC:L/PR:N/UI:N/S:U/C:N/I:N/A:N\"},{\"id\":50,\"element\":\"Function Code\",\"threat_description\":\"Exposure of code in transit reveals business logic and secrets.\",\"element_type\":\"Data Store\",\"stride\":\"Information Disclosure\",\"Mitre ATT&CK\":\"T1537: Transfer Data to Cloud Account\",\"OWASP Top 10\":\"A02:2021\",\"mitigation\":\"Encrypt transport channels; restrict access to package store.\",\"cvss_vector\":\"AV:N/AC:L/PR:N/UI:N/S:U/C:H/I:N/A:N\"},{\"id\":51,\"element\":\"Function Code\",\"threat_description\":\"Large code downloads slow or block function startup.\",\"element_type\":\"Data Stor